java.io.Serializable
public class CTRInit_SendTopAgents
extends jade.proto.AchieveREInitiator

The CTRInit_SendTopAgents represents the partner’s preselection protocol. This protocol sends a list of agents that are interested in participating to the CompTrust agent, in order to shorten this list to the most trustworthy agents only. This step will only take place if the EA-starter says so in his Negotiate request (which includes two parameters for this).

Author:
pbn, hlc
